; Coverage for format.cc %$ field reference error
; Triggered by %$0 or %$X (invalid field reference digit)

2024/01/15 Test
    Expenses:Food    $50.00
    Assets:Checking

; Test: %$0 is invalid (must be 1-9 or A-F)
test reg --format '%(amount)\n%/%$0\n' -> 1
__ERROR__
Error: %$ field reference must be a digit from 1-9
end test
